        <mxCell id="E-cl75kj5G9YbpEQe-Dy-79" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;align=center;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0a0a0a&quot; face=&quot;Google Sans, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;npm (Node Package Manager) is the primary tool used by JavaScript developersto discover, share, and manage code. It functions as both a massive online database (the Registry) and a command-line tool (the CLI).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
